Maintainer: EGVPI Team <CLIAR@worldbank.org>
Description: Provides a set of reproducible, modular functions to support the 
    ETL processing of the Country-Level Institutional Assessment and 
    Review (CLIAR) data. The package standardizes data cleaning, 
    metadata alignment, data quality controls, global benchmarking 
    (closeness-to-frontier CTF calculations), and coverage calculations 
    to ensure methodological consistency across institutional clusters 
    (PFM, HRM, Digital & Data, etc.). Functions integrate 
    external datasets (e.g., OECD, IMF, WDI, V-Dem) with World Bank metadata 
    standards, supporting downstream Shiny dashboards (cliarapp) and analytical workflows.
